threads.title: 820-00923 a1706 water damage
threads.message:
got corroded around u7650 and q5159 before i did something when plugin charger battery removed
fan spins very loud but no display few seconds it will stop spinning the fan.
after i clean corroded parts
can on once can see apple logo but after loading dead after i repeat cant turn on again.

usb meter got 20v 1.75amp
ppbus_g3h is 13v
PP3v3_s5 3.3v
PM_SLP_SUS_L 3.3v
SMC_ADAPTER_EN 3.4v
PM_BATLOW_L   3.3v
PCH_INTRUDER_L 2.8v

before and after replace u7650
23: 13v
12: 3.4v
13: 2v
22: 3.3v
29: 5.1v
21: 3.4v

nextstep?
